comment: Rubio (MIN) makes contact with Vucevic (ORL) that affects his SQBR.
[Incidental or immaterial] PXP shows Rubio (MIN) enter the area inside the three-point line prior to the free throw being released.
Ibaka (ORL) makes incidental contact with Bjelica (MIN) during rebounding.
LaVine (MIN) makes body to body contact with Watson (ORL) that affects his SQBR.
Gordon (ORL) maintains legal guarding position and legally contests Wiggins' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
LaVine (MIN) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Watson (ORL) that does not affect his SQBR.
Rubio (MIN) makes contact with Gordon's (ORL) body that affects his shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) sets the screen on Gordon (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Towns (MIN) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Vucevic (ORL) that does not affect his SQBR.

LO SLA shows Vucevic (ORL) fumble the basketball, regain possession and legally attempt to shoot. A player who is holding the ball and fumbles it out of his control may recover the ball and if his pivot foot moves when he recovers the ball, he must then pass or shoot.
Payton (ORL) makes contact with Rubio (MIN) that affects his SQBR.
Towns (MIN) sets the screen on Gordon (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Towns (MIN) legally contests Payton's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
